\begin_body

\begin_layout Title
gauge-theory
\end_layout

\begin_layout Author
Thomas Young
\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
非阿贝尔规范对称性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
平行移动算子
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在定域规范变换下，要使不同时空点上的场之间有物理意义的联系，
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

{
\backslash
color{red}{需要将一个时空点上的场移动到另一个点，然后进行比较}}
\end_layout

\end_inset

（如加减，标量积等操作。）这时，必须引入一个引子来补偿不同时空点上，规范变换之间的差异。这种移动操作可以通过引入
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

{
\backslash
color{red}{平行移动算子}}
\end_layout

\end_inset

来实现。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
自由的Dirac 场（电子场）的拉氏量：
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{L}_{0}\left(x\right)=\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\left(i\gamma^{\mu}\partial_{\mu}-m\right)\psi\left(x\right)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
整体对称性：
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\left(x\right)\to e^{i\alpha}\psi\left(x\right),\quad\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\to\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)e^{-i\alpha}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
局域对称性中的
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

依赖于坐标
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
从 x 移动到y的平行移动算子
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(y,x\right)$
\end_inset

满足性质：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U\left(y,x\right)\to e^{i\,\alpha\left(y\right)}U\left(y,x\right)e^{-i\,\alpha\left(x\right)}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
普通导数：
\begin_inset Formula $n^{\mu}\partial_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)=\lim_{\varepsilon\to0}\frac{1}{\varepsilon}\left(\psi\left(x+n\epsilon\right)-\psi\left(x\right)\right)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由于涉及到两个不同时空点上场的差。所以定域规范变换在两个时空点上是不同的，所以直接相减没有很好的定义。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
协变导数：
\begin_inset Formula $n^{\mu}D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)=\lim_{\varepsilon\to0}\frac{1}{\varepsilon}\left(\psi\left(x+n\epsilon\right)-U\left(x+n\varepsilon,x\right)\psi\left(x\right)\right)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
相当于移动到一起再相减。将无穷小平行移动算子在单位元附近作展开
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U\left(x+n\varepsilon,x\right)=1-i\varepsilon en^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(x\right)+O\left(\varepsilon^{2}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
含义：变化量正比于移动距离
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon n$
\end_inset

，比例系数为
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)=\partial_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)+ieA_{\mu}\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)=\left(\partial_{\mu}+ieA_{\mu}\left(x\right)\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这实际上给出了电磁场的几何含义：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
定域的
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(1\right)$
\end_inset

对称性自然引入了
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(1\right)$
\end_inset

规范场，它是一种联络场。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
有限平移算子
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果将无穷小平行移动沿某条路径
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{C}$
\end_inset

从
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

到
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

连续作用，则会生成一个有限的平行移动算子
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right)$
\end_inset

:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
U\left(x+\Delta x,x\right) & =1-ie\Delta x^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(x\right)+O\left(\Delta x^{2}\right)\\
 & \approx\exp\left[-ie\int_{x}^{x+\Delta x}\dif y^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(y\right)\right]
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right) & =U\left(y,y-\Delta x\right)U\left(y-\Delta x,y-2\Delta x\right)\cdots U\left(x+\Delta x,x\right)\\
 & \equiv\mathcal{P}\exp\left[-ie\int_{x,\mathcal{C}}^{y}\dif z^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(z\right)\right]
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
有限的平行移动算子
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right)$
\end_inset

是和路径
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{C}$
\end_inset

有关的，且满足如下关系：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right)U\left(x,y;\mathcal{C}\right) & =1\\
U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right)^{-1}=U\left(x,y;\mathcal{C}\right) & =U^{\dagger}\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
非定域规范不变算子（Wilson line）：
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}\left(y\right)\Gamma U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}\right)\psi\left(x\right)$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
规范场强是规范不变的：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
U\left(x,x;\mathcal{C}\right) & =U\left(x,y;\mathcal{C}_{1}\right)U\left(y,x;\mathcal{C}_{2}\right)\cdots U\left(x+\Delta x,x\right)\\
 & \equiv\mathcal{P}\exp\left[-ie\oint_{\mathcal{C}}\dif z^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(z\right)\right]=\exp\left[-ie\iint_{\partial\mathcal{C}}\dif\sigma^{\mu\nu}F_{\mu\nu}\right]
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
规范场强：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)=\partial_{\mu}A_{\nu}\left(x\right)-\partial_{\nu}A_{\mu}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

是规范不变的。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
非阿贝尔规范对称性–Yang–Mills 理论
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
假设两种费米子场
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{1}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{1}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

，它们的质量相同，则它们的自由拉氏量可以写作
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}_{0}=\bar{\psi}_{1}\left(i\gamma^{\mu}\partial-m\right)\psi_{1}+\bar{\psi}_{2}\left(i\gamma^{\mu}\partial-m\right)\psi_{2}\equiv\bar{\psi}\left(i\gamma^{\mu}\partial-m\right)\psi
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\psi\left(x\right) & =\left(\begin{array}{c}
\psi_{1}\left(x\right)\\
\psi_{2}\left(x\right)
\end{array}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{L}_{0}$
\end_inset


\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\xout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none
在整体的
\begin_inset Formula $SU\left(2\right)$
\end_inset

变换下不变：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{array}{ccc}
\psi\left(x\right)\to V\psi\left(x\right) & \bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\to\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\\
V,V^{\dagger}\in SU\left(2\right), & VV^{\dagger}=V^{\dagger}V=1 & \det V=1
\end{array}
\]

\end_inset

这个体系就有整体的
\begin_inset Formula $SU\left(2\right)$
\end_inset

对称性。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $SU\left(2\right)$
\end_inset

群：二维复空间的幺正幺模矩阵群，三个生成元
\begin_inset Formula $t^{a},a=1,2,3$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[t^{a},t^{b}\right]=i\varepsilon^{abc}t^{c},\qquad V=e^{i\theta^{a}t^{a}}\in SU\left(2\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
对于
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

维表示，生成元可以表示成
\begin_inset Formula $n\times n$
\end_inset

的矩阵，我们经常用
\begin_inset Formula $T^{a}$
\end_inset

来表示，以与基础表示矩阵
\begin_inset Formula $t^{a}$
\end_inset

区分，相应的
\begin_inset Formula $SU\left(2\right)$
\end_inset

的变换矩阵为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{n\times n}=\exp[i\theta^{a}T^{a}]
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
SU(N)定域规范对称性
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果仿照QED的情形，我们将上述整体非阿贝尔变换定域化，即令群参数
\begin_inset Formula $\theta^{a}$
\end_inset

是时空的函数，
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V\left(x\right)\in SU\left(2\right),\qquad V\left(x\right)=\exp^{i\theta^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{L}_{0}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

在这种定域变换下，不再是不变的（偏导数也作用于
\begin_inset Formula $V\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

）
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\mathcal{L}_{0}\left(x\right) & \to\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)\left(i\gamma^{\mu}\partial_{\mu}\right)V\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)-m\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)\\
 & \bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\left(i\gamma^{\mu}\partial_{\mu}-m\right)\psi\left(x\right)+i\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\gamma^{\mu}V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)\left(\partial_{\mu}V\left(x\right)\right)\psi\left(x\right)\\
 & \mathcal{L}_{0}\left(x\right)++i\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\gamma^{\mu}V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)\left(\partial_{\mu}V\left(x\right)\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
平行移动算子，从
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

移动到
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

的平行移动算子
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(y,x\right)$
\end_inset

满足性质：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U\left(y,x\right)\to V\left(y\right)U\left(y,x\right)v^{\dagger}\left(x\right),V\left(x\right)=e^{i\theta^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
无穷小平行移动算子：在单位元附近作无穷小展开
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
U\left(x+n\varepsilon,x\right) & =I+i\varepsilon gn^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(x\right)+O\left(\varepsilon\right)\\
 & =I+i\varepsilon gn^{\mu}A_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}+O\left(\varepsilon^{2}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
协变导数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
n^{\mu}D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right) & =\lim_{\varepsilon\to0}\frac{1}{\varepsilon}\left[\psi\left(x+n\varepsilon\right)-U\left(x+n\varepsilon,x\right)\psi\left(x\right)\right]\\
 & =\lim_{\varepsilon\to0}\frac{1}{\varepsilon}\left[\psi\left(x\right)+\varepsilon n^{\mu}\partial_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)-\psi\left(x\right)-ig\varepsilon n^{\mu}A_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}\psi\left(x\right)\right]\\
 & =n^{\mu}\left(\partial_{\mu}-igA_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{\mu}=\partial_{\mu}-igA_{\mu}\left(x\right)=\partial_{\mu}-igA_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

:规范耦合常数
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\left(x\right)=A_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}$
\end_inset

称为规范场，它是一种联络场。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

的规范变换性质：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left.\begin{array}{c}
U\left(y,x\right)\to V\left(y\right)U\left(y,x\right)v^{\dagger}\left(x\right)\\
U\left(x+n\varepsilon,x\right)=I+i\varepsilon gn^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(x\right)+O\left(\varepsilon^{2}\right)
\end{array}\right\}  & \to\\
I+ig\varepsilon n^{\mu}A_{\mu}\left(x\right)\to & I+ig\varepsilon n^{\mu}\left(V\left(x\right)A_{\mu}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)+\frac{i}{g}V\left(x\right)\partial_{\mu}V^{\mu}\left(x\right)\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

的规范变换性质（重要）：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A_{\mu}\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)A_{\mu}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)+\frac{i}{g}V\left(x\right)\partial_{\mu}V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

不是规范协变的，而
\begin_inset Formula $D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

是规范协变的
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{\mu}\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)D_{\mu}\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
进一步地有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right) & \to V\left(x\right)D_{\mu}\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)=V\left(x\right)D_{\mu}\left(x\right)\left(v^{\dagger}\left(x\right)V\left(x\right)\right)\psi\left(x\right)\\
 & =V(x)D_{\mu}(x)V^{\dagger}(x)V(x)\psi(x)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{\mu}(x)\to V(x)D_{\mu}(x)V^{\dagger}(x)
\]

\end_inset

进一步地，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[D_{\mu}\left(x\right),D_{\mu}\left(y\right)\right]\psi\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)\left[D_{\mu}\left(x\right),D_{\mu}\left(y\right)\right]V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)V\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[D_{\mu}\left(x\right),D_{\mu}\left(y\right)\right]\to V\left(x\right)\left[D_{\mu}\left(x\right),D_{\mu}\left(y\right)\right]V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset

定义规范场强
\begin_inset Formula $F_{\mu\nu}\equiv F_{\mu\nu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}=\frac{i}{g}\left[D_{\mu}\left(x\right),D_{\nu}\left(x\right)\right]$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
规范场强用规范场表示：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left[D_{\mu},D_{\nu}\right]\psi & =\left[\partial_{\mu}-igA_{\mu},\partial_{\nu}-igA_{\nu}\right]\psi=-ig\left[\partial_{\mu}A_{\nu}-\partial_{\nu}A_{\mu}-ig\left[A_{\mu},A_{\nu}\right]\right]\psi\equiv-igF_{\mu\nu}\psi
\end{align*}

\end_inset

所以，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{\mu\nu}=\partial_{\mu}A_{\nu}-\partial_{\nu}A_{\mu}-ig\left[A_{\mu},A_{\nu}\right]
\]

\end_inset

利用群生成元的对易关系：
\begin_inset Formula $\left[t^{a},t^{b}\right]=if^{abc}t^{c}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F_{\mu\nu}^{a}\left(x\right)=\partial_{\mu}A_{\nu}^{a}\left(x\right)-\partial_{\nu}A_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)+gf^{abc}A_{\mu}^{b}\left(x\right)A_{\nu}^{c}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
协变导数作用在自伴表示上：对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $B\left(x\right)=B^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
D_{\mu}B\left(x\right) & =\partial_{\mu}B\left(x\right)-ig\left[A_{\mu},B\right]\\
\left(D_{\mu}\right)_{b}^{a}B^{b}\left(x\right) & =\partial_{\mu}B^{a}+gf^{abc}A_{\mu}^{b}B^{c}=\partial_{\mu}B^{a}-igA_{\mu}^{b}\left(T^{b}\right)^{ac}B^{c}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
if^{abc} & =T^{b,ac}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
T^{b,ac}=-if^{b,ac}
\]

\end_inset

省略洛伦兹指标，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
D^{ab}B^{b}\left(x\right) & =\partial B^{a}+gf^{abc}A^{b}B^{c}=\partial B^{a}-igA^{b}T^{b,ac}B^{c}\\
 & =\partial B^{a}+igT^{a,bc}A^{b}B^{c}
\end{align}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
小结：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
D_{\mu}=\partial_{\mu}-igA_{\mu}\left(x\right)=\partial_{\mu}-igA_{\mu}^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
有限的非阿贝尔变换，
\begin_inset Formula $V\left(x\right)=e^{i\theta^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}\in G}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{array}{c}
\text{\ensuremath{\psi\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)=e^{i\theta^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}}\psi\left(x\right)}}\\
D_{\mu}\left(x\right)\psi\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)=e^{i\theta^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}}D_{\mu}\psi\left(x\right)\\
D_{\mu}\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)D_{\mu}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)\\
F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)
\end{array}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

但是规范场
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

不是规范协变的：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A_{\mu}\left(x\right)\to V\left(x\right)A_{\mu}\left(x\right)V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)+\frac{i}{g}V\left(x\right)\partial_{\mu}V^{\dagger}\left(x\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
无穷小非阿贝尔变换 
\begin_inset Formula $V\left(x\right)=1+i\varepsilon^{a}t^{a}+O\left(\varepsilon^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{array}{c}
\text{\ensuremath{\psi\left(x\right)\to\left(1+i\varepsilon^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}\right)\psi\left(x\right)\Rightarrow\delta\psi=i\varepsilon^{a}t^{a}\psi\left(x\right)}}\end{array}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\to\left(1+i\varepsilon^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}\right)F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)\left(1-i\varepsilon^{a}\left(x\right)t^{a}\right)\\
=F_{\mu\nu}\left(x\right)-i\varepsilon^{a}(x)\left[F_{\mu\nu}(x),t^{a}\right]\\
\Rightarrow\delta F_{\mu\nu}(x)=i\varepsilon^{a}(x)\left[t^{a},F_{\mu\nu}(x)\right]
\end{align}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
A(x)\to\left(1+i\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}\right)A_{\mu}(x)\left(1-i\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}\right)\\
+\frac{i}{g}\left(1+i\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}\right)\partial_{\mu}\left(1-i\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}\right)\\
=A_{\mu}(x)+i\varepsilon^{a}\left[t^{a},A_{\mu}\left(x\right)\right]+\frac{1}{g}\partial_{\mu}\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}-\frac{1}{g}\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}\left(\partial_{\mu}1\right)\\
=A_{\mu}(x)+\frac{1}{g}\partial_{\mu}\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}-\left[iA_{\mu}\left(x\right),\varepsilon^{a}t^{a}\right]
\end{align}

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon(x)=\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}$
\end_inset

，利用
\begin_inset Formula $\left[t^{a},t^{b}\right]=if^{abc}t^{c}$
\end_inset

，所以，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\delta A_{\mu}(x)=\frac{1}{g}\partial_{\mu}\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}-\left[iA_{\mu}\left(x\right),\varepsilon^{a}t^{a}\right]\\
=\frac{1}{g}\partial_{\mu}\varepsilon^{a}(x)t^{a}+f^{bac}A_{\mu}^{b}\left(x\right)\varepsilon^{a}t^{c}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\xout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none
若写成分量形式，得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\delta A_{\mu}^{a}=\frac{1}{g}\partial_{\mu}\varepsilon^{a}(x)-f^{abc}\varepsilon^{b}A_{\mu}^{c}\left(x\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
end of file
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
end of file
\end_layout

